
=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.10 ***
=====================================================================

--> ScalarCustFld included

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.9 ***
=====================================================================

--> MagLED, RedDensGrad, and RoSE fields included.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.8a ***
=====================================================================

--> Using figlet name.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.8 ***
=====================================================================

--> The log file now includes the number of primitives of the 
      wave function

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.7 ***
=====================================================================

--> Added the molecular electrostatic potential to the properties
      evaluated.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.6 ***
=====================================================================

--> Added output information in a logfile. dtkcube now (upon request),
    writes extra-information in the log file.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.5 ***
=====================================================================

Some changes to the help menu and support for long command line
options (e.g. --help, and --version).

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.4 ***
=====================================================================

Minor spelling corrections...

--> The class wavefunction now correctly reads files with a number
      of primitives equal to a multiple of 20
--> The class bondnetwork foresees the cases where 
      maxBondDist have not been determined due to non of the
      atoms are linked (according to the Van Der Walls sum criteria,
      i.e., the algorithm for drawing CPK/ball&stick molecules)



=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.3 ***
=====================================================================

Added the property: Magnitude of the Gradient of LOL

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.2 ***
=====================================================================

Fixed Bugs: 

  --> The output name is now set correctly. (A set of characters
        are added to the end of the input name for setting the
        output file name.)
  --> The current version flag is also displayed in the help menu.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.1 ***
=====================================================================

Fixed Bugs: 

  --> A wfn file containing a single atom is now handled correctly
  --> Now the compression have to be explicitly requested from the command line
        (using -z option). 
  --> Several functions were added to the wavefunctionclass.* files,
        these changes do not affect the program denscube per se.


=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.0 ***
=====================================================================

First release of the program.

Known bugs:
  --> The program does not handle single atom wave function files.
  --> The compression is performed by default
